+# Codex Writer Findings — CartView
+Chain: cartview-260415-105013-e600
+
+## Findings
+1. [P0] `getOrderStatus` drops `internal_code` — `pages/PublicMenu/useTableSession.jsx:797-811` resolves `stage_id` through `stagesMap`, but it only returns `{ icon, label, color }`. That leaves `CartView` without a stable signal for terminal `OrderStages.internal_code === 'finish'`, so Fix 1 cannot be implemented stage-first. FIX: return `internal_code: stage.internal_code || null` for mapped stages and `internal_code: null` in the fallback object.
+2. [P0] `statusBuckets` still groups by legacy `o.status` instead of stage state — `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:427-435` buckets orders only from `(o.status || 'new').toLowerCase()`, while the prompt’s real source of truth is `stage_id.internal_code`. Orders moved to the terminal `finish` stage can therefore stay in `in_progress` instead of `served`. The legacy cancellation filter is also still hard-coded at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:418`, which matches the prompt’s CV-BUG-06 backlog note. FIX: make `statusBuckets` stage-first via `getOrderStatus(o).internal_code`, keep `o.status` only as a fallback for legacy rows, and leave the line-418 cancellation cleanup as backlog-only.
+3. [P1] The requested `Мои / Стол` tab split is not implemented — `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1-6` imports no `Tabs` primitives, and `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:776-883` still renders the old collapsible `Заказы стола` card plus a separate `Счёт стола` card. The drawer therefore keeps the mixed single-column flow that Fix 2 is supposed to replace. FIX: import `Tabs`, `TabsList`, `TabsTrigger`, `TabsContent` from `@/components/ui/tabs` and wrap the current section-3/4/5 content in one top-level tabset with `defaultValue="my"`.
+4. [P1] The totals layout is still the pre-tab model — `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:482-491` computes `tableOrdersTotal` from other guests only, `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:794` displays that partial amount in the section-5 header, and the full `tableTotal` appears only in a standalone card at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:873-879`. That does not satisfy Fix 2’s requested split of guest-only total in `Мои` and grand total inside `Стол`. FIX: keep the guest total in `Мои`, add the mini `Счёт стола` switch row there, and move the grand-total presentation into the `Стол` tab instead of the old standalone card.
+5. [P2] Fix 3 and deferred Fix 4 are still unresolved in the current structure — `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:501` defines `showTableOrdersSection`, but it only gates the old table-orders card; there is no `showTableOrdersSection ? <Tabs ...> : <>{my content}</>` wrapper for the single-guest path required by Fix 3. Separately, the only `scrollIntoView` calls at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:940` and `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1014` are rating-flow helpers, which confirms the prompt’s deferred note: `CartView` still has no `openReason` or status-change trigger for safe scroll-to-order auto-open. FIX: add the single-guest tabs bypass when implementing Fix 2, and keep the scroll-to-order work deferred under BACKLOG #324 until parent context exists.
